stories.description: The Mosque Admin searches for inventory items using a specific vendor name to view the available stock details.
stories.expected_outcome:
The inventory table updates to show only items supplied by 'aifamart'.

VALIDATION: Assert: table row count changes to show only items with 'Nama Vendor' as 'aifamart'.

steps.target: Step 3: Verify table updates to show only items from 'aifamart'

stories.description: The Super Admin adds a new stock entry to the inventory system, specifying details such as quantity, purchase price, warranty, and supplier.
stories.expected_outcome:
A new stock entry is added to the inventory with the specified details.

VALIDATION: Assert: new entry appears in the inventory table with 'Nama Produk' as 'Peci' and 'Nama Vendor' as 'aifamart'.

steps.target: Step 10: Verify new entry in inventory table

stories.description: The Mosque Admin activates an inactive inventory item to make it available for transactions.
stories.expected_outcome:
The status of the selected inventory item changes to 'Active'.

VALIDATION: Assert: status of the item changes to 'Active' in the inventory table.

steps.target: Step 2: Click more_vert on an inactive item

stories.description: The Ministry Admin filters the inventory items by a specific category to view relevant stock details.
stories.expected_outcome:
The inventory table displays only items under the 'Perlengkapan Ibadah' category.

VALIDATION: Assert: table shows only items with 'categoryId' as 'Perlengkapan Ibadah'.

steps.target: Step 3: Verify table updates to show only relevant items

stories.description: The Super Admin uploads a document related to a specific inventory item for record-keeping.
stories.expected_outcome:
The document is successfully uploaded and linked to the inventory item.

VALIDATION: Assert: uploaded document appears in the inventory item details.

steps.target: Step 2: Click more_vert on an item
Step 5: Verify document is linked to item
